    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "Moreover, I figured out the cause, the project is incorrectly detecting the root. I have a git project with a folder called `contracts`, within which is the foundry project, including `remappings.txt`, with a `pwd` of `contracts/`, the project root is incorrectly detected as `../`, which doesn't contain any solidity code. The `remappings.txt` override works successfully if I specify the full path to `contracts/` as a `--root` argument to the tool.",
